        <!-- <letterText>\n\n&lt;color="#808080"&gt;"In order to for a better tomorrow to be built, we must pave the way. Defense, labor and projection is not cheap however, taxes shall be needed in order to pay for this great road into the future!"&lt;/color&gt; ~ President Kimball</letterText> -->
